Metacritic scraper to generate review datasets for games, movies, music, and tv

Dependencies:
	PHP CLI
	Bash
	
Options:
	REQUIRED:
		1) Number of pages deep to parse off of the score browser (page 0 is the highest scores)
		2) Name of the output file
	OPTIONAL:
		3) Media type [case sensitive]; movies, games, music, tv
		4) Sub-Media type (only applies when 'games' are specified) [case sensitive]; ps3, xbox360, wii, pc, psp, ds, ps2